  "1877190": {
    "name": "Astrogon",
    "steam_appid": 1877190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "在墙壁和障碍物之间跳跃和飞行。<br>避免触及会杀死你的东西，并到达传送门。<br>掌握精确和战略，否则就得死。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/ed7619990365990f053c207ea75ebf79.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/ed7619990365990f053c207ea75ebf79.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/ed7619990365990f053c207ea75ebf79.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直觉游戏：抓住正确的球体。</h2>触摸红色球体并变成红色，你就会安全地触摸到红色的墙壁。<br><br>蓝色的也是如此。<br>触摸绿色球体可以 &quot;额外跳跃&quot;，你会跳到下一个台阶。<br>触摸黄色球体可以冲刺，并向下、向侧面或向天空飞去。<br>要精确和有策略，否则就得死。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/cb0ba2e37ef85c635780b5d734dc4625.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/cb0ba2e37ef85c635780b5d734dc4625.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/cb0ba2e37ef85c635780b5d734dc4625.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人模式：每个维度的难度越来越大。</h2>5个维度。每个维度有16个级别。<br><br>原子、分子、行星、银河系、超级新星。(更多维度即将到来)<br>一个具有挑战性的单人冒险。<br>掌握精确和战略，否则就得死。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/18055bfafbd5925cb7bdfde03c2c3d1d.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/18055bfafbd5925cb7bdfde03c2c3d1d.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/18055bfafbd5925cb7bdfde03c2c3d1d.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创意模式：创建你自己的地图。</h2>通过直观的关卡编辑器，创建并上传你自己的关卡。<br><br>其他玩家会玩，喜欢，评论，并会关注你，成为他们最喜欢的Astrogon创造者。<br>因此，请发挥创意，制作出疯狂的关卡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/50325d25055b09e0c9d8ca29208306b8.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/50325d25055b09e0c9d8ca29208306b8.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/50325d25055b09e0c9d8ca29208306b8.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限的可重复性：一生都不足以玩遍所有的关卡。</h2>顶级关卡、特色创作者和热门关卡的排名。<br><br>超过20.000个关卡，已经有世界各地的创作者提供。<br>让你的名字成为一个传奇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/2d351f025b404a3ff352c618dd0b6de4.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/2d351f025b404a3ff352c618dd0b6de4.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/2d351f025b404a3ff352c618dd0b6de4.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人模式：与其他玩家对战</h2> 实时击败其他玩家。<br><br>挑战你的朋友，或与来自世界各地的其他玩家进行比赛。<br>非常适合激烈的直播会议。<br>获得排名，成为最好的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/ca28f90e18885766af4ba319dfc9d227.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/ca28f90e18885766af4ba319dfc9d227.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/ca28f90e18885766af4ba319dfc9d227.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速运行模式：时间就是生命</h2> 在最短的时间内连续完成16关。<br><br>国际排名和世界纪录危在旦夕。<br>要快速而精确，否则就会死亡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/e579b014846d113d8ed34def83040ef3.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/e579b014846d113d8ed34def83040ef3.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/e579b014846d113d8ed34def83040ef3.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一款具有竞争力的硬核精密平板电脑</h2> 国际排行榜，每个模式都有排名。<br><br>独奏模式，创意模式，多人游戏，快速运行。<br>如果你的排名高，就会很受欢迎，并被大量关注。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/cb2612b96c3a004559ee7391f8e0c541.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/cb2612b96c3a004559ee7391f8e0c541.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/cb2612b96c3a004559ee7391f8e0c541.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏中的皮肤! </h2>赢得最多的星星来获得你最喜欢的皮肤。<br><br>Ultraspinner、Transformer、Alieneye和其他许多皮肤。<br>皮肤不会给你的技能，但会给你的风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/2a932872423e0e332b04943941607b68.poster.avif?t=1686916453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/2a932872423e0e332b04943941607b68.webm?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877190/extras/2a932872423e0e332b04943941607b68.mp4?t=1686916453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
